reviewText:
Proboscis is a really great film.  I actually laughed, and had a good  time.  I was really amazed abouth this, as I knew the star from grade  school.  It was better than most film from hollywood, and is worth seeing  again and again.
It has action, blood, comic relief.  Well put  together, the story line even made sense.  I bought this as soon as I heard  about it, and I encourage you to do the same.
